description: Redevelopment of the site to provide 137 residential units (Use Class C3) comprising 51 houses and 86 apartments ranging from 2-5 storeys, 158 car parking spaces, cycle parking, landscaping, access improvements and other associated development. Extension of the Edgware Eruv to include the site and installation of poles and wire gateway. (SUBJECT TO LEGAL AGREEMENT DATED 1 APRIL 2021)
